(199, 1, '2014-08-10 19:02:00', '2014-08-10 19:02:00', '&nbsp;\n\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Take Offs</h2>\n\n<h4>What the client <em>(You)</em> provides:</h4>\n\n<ul>\n<li>We would need job request with all pertinent job and client contact information (See job start page)</li>\n<li>We would need to  have to have a brief scope statement or description so we get you a take off on just what your interested in and nothing else.</li>\n<li>We need your bid date so we can get you the "take offs"  back yo you in time so it can be used to estimate work, create budgets or quantify back ups for change orders, on time.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>What we provide you:</h4>\n\n<ul>\n<li>A graphical take off on the digital plan you provide</li>\n<li>A quantity takeoff form outlining all the elements called out on the plan. We can also do more customized take offs providing take offs the way your company like to see information.</li>\n</ul>\n\nThe takeoff is provided on an Excel spread sheet and can be expanded to so re-bar detailing and concrete yardage and anything else you want to see is noted.\n\n<blockquote>\n  <center><strong>IF YOU CAN''T MEASURE IT YOU CAN''T CONTROL IT</strong></center>\n</blockquote>', 'Take Offs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-10 19:02:00', '2014-08-10 19:02:00', '&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Take Offs</h2>\r\n#### What the client _(You)_ provides: #### \r\n* We would need job request with all pertinent job and client contact information (See job start page)\r\n* We would need to  have to have a brief scope statement or description so we get you a take off on just what your interested in and nothing else.\r\n* We need your bid date so we can get you the "take offs"  back yo you in time so it can be used to estimate work, create budgets or quantify back ups for change orders, on time.\r\n\r\n#### What we provide you: ####\r\n* A graphical take off on the digital plan you provide\r\n* A quantity takeoff fo