(32, 1, '2014-07-12 09:36:14', '2014-07-12 09:36:14', 'So what’s that got to do you? I can help. I have been working in the concrete trade for over 30 years doing all kinds of concrete work. I am available and I don’t need to be a permanent overhead cost either. Through the miracle of internet and e-mail we can work remotely. Results, that''s what you need, more work. More sales are good but really what is needed is to work smarter. Work with a lower overhead but with added value. These are the services can be provide; Estimates, Proposals with clearly defined scopes of work. Prospecting for work, project development for new work. Analyzing your existing production values and writing up standards with specific procedures or products with the goal of increasing efficiency and safety in the field.\r\n', 'Benefits', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-12 09:36:14', '2014-07-12 09:36:14', '', 18, 'http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/?p=32', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
