(56, 2, '2015-10-07 07:33:35', '2015-10-07 07:33:35', '&nbsp;\n\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Concrete Estimating and Project Management</h2>\n\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Annenberg.jpg"><img class="alignleft wp-image-78 fill-screen-on-mobile" src="http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Annenberg-200x150.jpg" alt="Annenberg" width="132" height="99" /></a></p>\n\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n\nConcrete Estimating and Project Management when you need it.\n\nWe can increase sales, production and profits by providing low-cost, accurate, detailed project take-offs in a timely fashion, faster and more efficiently than can be done in-house.\n\nWe help small concrete companies increase sales and profits by providing an accurate color-coded digital take-off that easily identifies the scope of work, communicating a visual representation of the takeoff. We go a step further with a color-coded legend on the pages of the document to enhance the understanding of the takeoff. These documents can then be used to estimate the work accurately.\n\nPlans are quantified, broken down into logical work structures so that all you need to do is determine the value of the work based on your production rates and how your company does its work.  We can in most cases have this information back to you in 24 hrs.', 'Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-10-07 07:33:35', '2015-10-07 07:33:35', '', 1, 'http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/1-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
