(163, 2, '2014-08-03 23:00:41', '2014-08-03 23:00:41', '&nbsp;\n\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Experience</h2>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, Palatino;">I have worked in the concrete trade for over 30 years as an Estimator and Project Manager on challenging projects all across the Western US, Hawaii and Mexico.\n</span><span style="font-family: Georgia, Palatino;">My experience is taking a design idea, building projects on time, and on budget, meeting the client’s requirements. I have the experience to anticipate problems, control risk, from pre-construction to closing the project.\n</span>I am a certified project management professional (PMP) from the Project Management Institute as well as a CDT Certification from the Construction Specifications Institute.</p>\n\n<center> <a href="http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/aci.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-134 size-logo-thumb" src="http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/aci-100x56.png" alt="" width="100" height="56" /></a>          <a href="http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/csi_logo_colored.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-133 size-logo-thumb" src="http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/csi_logo_colored-100x58.png" alt="" width="100" height="58" />          <img class="alignnone wp-image-132" src="http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/pmi_cleaned-100x36.png" alt="" width="128" height="46" /></a></center>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Which is all cool, but I love concrete.</em> I love to form it, pour it and finish it. Teaching, coaching, building teams and having fun creating beautiful concrete space, which is what we do.</p>\n</blockquote>', 'Experience', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-08-03 23:00:41', '2014-08-03 23:00:41', '', 20, 'http://www.mostlyconcretellc.com/20-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', ''